title: Shoot the Boot - David Wise and Seb Toots
description:
Sometimes even the best of ideas can go wrong, and sometimes they are just bad ideas to begin with.

Watch what happens when O’Neill athletes David Wise and Seb Toots “attempt” a follow shot at Nine Knights. 

Boys, welcome to the #unreasonable award contention!
